# Prisma — DO commit migrations (`packages/db/prisma/migrations/**`); they
# are part of the source of truth. The negation below makes that explicit so
# nothing accidentally ignores them via a broader rule.
!packages/db/prisma/migrations/
!packages/db/prisma/migrations/**
